text: Richard Phelps (born 21 November 1965) is a British rower. He competed in the men's eight event at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1965 births Category:Living people Category:British male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Great Britain Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Rowers from Greater London
